title: Bring your family home to this Res Lease in Austin. 2 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ['Meticulously updated, spacious 2/2 stunner, one block off South Congress in the heart of Travis Heights!', 'This unique, luxurious end unit has a privacy forward floor plan with generous bedrooms located on opposite ends of the living space.', 'Kitchen boasts Bose Butcher Block Counters, subway tile backsplash, white cabinetry and stainless steel appliances.', 'Bathrooms feature floating Carrara marble vanities and bountiful built-in storage.', 'Copious closet space, abundant natural light, dual access private balcony, a fireplace and beautiful, durable wood plank flooring all highlight this gorgeous unit!', 'Separate utility room off kitchen with full sized washer/dryer connections.', 'Dedicated exterior storage closet.', 'Serene, quiet, park-like setting with ample parking and two separate grassy areas for outdoor enjoyment.', 'No through traffic on this quiet residential street.', "Walk to South Congress shopping and dining and just a stone's throw to downtown!", 'Two minutes to HEB, easy access to the Blunn Creek trail, Lady Bird Lake, Zilker, 290, I-35, 360, Mopac and Lamar.', 'You will adore this beautiful space and fantastic location!', ' *** Send Text Message FEDERICO to', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Federico Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 4652244)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas, All Prices)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'PRICES ARE SUBJECT TO CHANGE DAILY/PICS MAY NOT REFLECT EXACT UNIT']
